# --- LLM keys (at least one is recommended) ----------------------------------

# DeepSeek V4 Pro — top recommendation (1M context, frontier quality, cheapest
# top-tier model right now: $0.435/M input / $0.87/M output through May 31 2026).
# Get a key at https://platform.deepseek.com/api_keys
# Used by the few-shot fraud classifier specifically.
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=
# DEEPSEEK_MODEL=deepseek-v4-pro       # or deepseek-v4-flash for cheaper inference
# DEEPSEEK_REASONING_EFFORT=high       # low | high | max | disabled
# DEEPSEEK_BASE_URL=https://api.deepseek.com

# Google Gemini — generous free tier; gemini-2.5-flash works on free, pro is paid-only.
# Get a free key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash

# Optional fallback provider:
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4.1-mini

# Force a specific provider (deepseek | gemini | openai | ensemble | heuristic).
# "ensemble" runs all configured providers in parallel and merges findings —
# requires ≥2 keys to be useful. Leave blank for auto-routing.
# LLM_PROVIDER=
# LLM_PROVIDER=ensemble

# --- SEC EDGAR ---------------------------------------------------------------
# Required by SEC's automated-access policy. Use your real name & email.
SEC_USER_AGENT=Your Name your.email@example.com
